MetaTile: Create Campaign Monitor Integrations | Marketing Automation | Cyclr
MetaDescription: Help to enhance your users' email marketing campaigns & connect their data to your business application with Campaign Monitor integration from Cyclr.
Content:
Campaign Monitor’s powerful email marketing platform includes tools to create personalised and targeted campaigns that your customers will love. But can you help enhance these campaigns with your application's data?

With Cyclr you can. create your own automation workflows, with our drag and drop builder, and let your users connect your app with their Campaign Monitor account.
